/**
 * Description: Multiply polynomials of ints for any modulus $<2^{31}$.
 * For XOR convolution ignore \texttt{m} within \texttt{fft}.
 * Time: O(N\log N)
 * Source:
 * KACTL
 * (https://github.com/kth-competitive-programming/kactl/blob/master/content/numerical/NumberTheoreticTransform.h)
 * https://cp-algorithms.com/algebra/fft.html
